t he did - I think that he threw his - he had - he was in his high chair, you know, and I was feeding him and I dropped the - spoon for a bit you know and he took the - saucer and upset it. And I gave him a slap on the hand. But he was - I was never one -
 I never believe in physical violence. I always tried to - my husband used to - resort to - hitting them you know. But I said to him one day, look Hal - I cannot endure - seeing you t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
