at I can play as well as what I can do really. I make up hymns you know, I can make up hymns like billyo. Yes, I can sit down and play a hymn where I - oh I've made up lots of them, but I have written them down and seve - several of them I've quite forgot
ten but there's one or two I - I can remember quite well now.
